  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then as far as my eye could see, I saw the earth rise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I started running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And by time I reached the road, there were 11 craters-- 11 holes was where I was sitting, where I was watching.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I went back, we had baked potatoes from the shrapnels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And underground was a radar station.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under the potato field.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Underneath, yeah, because there was an airport not far from there, a military airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've seen American planes shot down, American pilots shot in the air before they reached the ground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were parachuted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- parachute, they were floating down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the next thing you saw is the SS with the motorcycles coming into the fields.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before they reached the ground, they killed them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They shot him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They stripped him of his stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how good these people were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
